  startId: LATENIGHT_R1
  nodes:
  - id: LATENIGHT_R1
    speaker: Ally Quinn
    line: "My contact showed up late and ordered the biggest thing on the menu.
      Over a burger and a lot of nervous glances at the door, they gave me
      a name. A different name — one the college never used."
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 792b5f88f6dd2724d84b6954cc0b5fad,
      type: 3}
    emotion: 4
    voiceClip: {fileID: 0}
    waitForAudio: 0
    requiresFlag:
    skipIfFlagMissing: 1
    setsFlag:
    nextId: LATENIGHT_R2
    choices: []
  - id: LATENIGHT_R2
    speaker: Ally Quinn
    line: "If that name is real, the enrollment is a cover. The Ghost Student
      didn't disappear. They were hiding. This isn't a missing persons case
      anymore."
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 792b5f88f6dd2724d84b6954cc0b5fad,
